body_html:
Hello,

Thanks for the quick replies. Other tests also fail with the same error. I checked my version of numpy (using >>>import numpy; numpy.version.version : 1.10.1), and was unable to find another (but I'm unfamiliar with how the modules are organized on that machine).

I ended up just compiling with my new op, and it works. However, if someone wants to help debug bazel-test, I'm happy to run more tests.

Best,
Yacine
